	<properties>
		<title>ICAT Java Client Installation</title>
	</properties>

	<body>

		<section name="Installation">

			<p>There are two files that should be made available to those wishing
				to use the ICAT client:
			</p>
			<dl>
				<dt><a href="${repoUrl}/org/icatproject/icat.client/${project.version}/icat.client-${project.version}.jar">icat.client-${project.version}.jar</a></dt>
				<dd>the client library which the user should add to the
					classpath.
				</dd>
                <dt><a href="${repoUrl}/org/icatproject/icat.client/${project.version}/icat.client-${project.version}-sources.jar">icat.client-${project.version}-sources.jar</a></dt>
				<dd>the source code of the client, which is especially useful
					when developing within an IDE.
				</dd>
			</dl>
		</section>
	</body>
